node.text:
So many amazing memories with Uncle D. Our time in Japan together will always hold a special place in my heart. 
.
Derek Ho was honored today at Pipeline -where he was king.  Hundreds if not over 1000 people gathered for a beautiful ceremony and paddle out to lay his ashes.  By official decree today is officially now Derek K Ho day in Hawaii!! 
.
Always love you Uncle Derek and the entire Ho Ohana. 
.
 #aloha #alohaderekho #derekkhoday #rainbow @freesurfmag @derekho1980 #surfing

So many have dedicated their life to seeing this dream become a reality!!! Thank you to everyone who was apart of this. Every positive thought from everyone around the world made this happen!!! THANK YOU!!

Without this planet we will all die. It is time we unite for the the greater good of humanity. Together we can make a difference. Every time you spend even a $1 you are either promoting the current single us plastic situation or protesting it. Every time you put food in your mouth you are either supporting local, organic agriculture or you are supporting deforestation, poisoned soil and a plethora of other challenges. Every moment of every day you are making a choice. So if you a celebrating EARTH DAY then make a commitment to make earth day choices every day!!!
.
.
.
#foreverforward #bringyourlife #bringyourkids #getoutside #earthfocus #earthday2021

Mavericks!!!
This was a fun one, 
I remember this day well, @kealiihawaii and I towed for hours. The fog was so thick we had to wait on the beach all morning 
We finally decided to go for it and drive through the harbor in the thick fog hugging the jetty 
We somehow got through to the line up 
It was a miracle, there was a big hole in the sky right around the lineup everywhere else is socked in!
@jamie_mitcho was out among a few of the boys, the Mavericks crew.
Earlier that morning I took @john_john_florence  out for his first look at Mavs
As we pulled up we saw @darrylfleavirostko coming down a bomb, he falls back and does this crazy lay back basically gets munched by the wave and somehow Pops back to his feet and makes it John John sitting on the back of my ski grab me tight and said I got the shivers from that one 
That’s when I quickly rushed back and I got Kealii. 
I remember my goal was to get barreled but this wave as I got to the bottom I was basically rolling up the windows on my heels and I couldn’t bottom turn 
I did the exactly same thing on the next wave every time came up smiling was so fun so many good waves Kealii was killing it surfing with effortless ease.

node.text: Maybe one day I will find the words to describe my amazing wife @mamaunearthed as eloquently as one of my best friends @khalilrafati did … #repost This Goddess is Nicole. What’s wrong with us???
CHALLENGE !!!! This month is @plasticfreejuly … we challenge everyone out there, including ourselves, to choose one plastic thing in our daily life and replace it with something single use plastic free. Please share below and tag someone who is ready to eliminate single use plastic!! SWIPE left to see photos of our home and ways we have gone single use plastic free:
* how many of your supplements are plastic free? Can you replace with a plastic free brand? @fe.earthtobody for CBD and @moonjuice for elixirs. 
* the easiest way to reduce single use plastic is a reusable water bottle!!! @hydroflask 
* in our bathroom we make our product as often as possible but life is busy. We use @davidsnaturaltoothpaste or @bite , always use a bamboo brush, and loving our @bewellow deodorant @rawelementsusa sunscreen
* super proud of @mamaunearthed to have gotten rid of all plastic in the shower. She only uses bar shampoo and conditioner @vioribeauty 
* and lastly our kitchen. We eliminated sponges and only use @swedishdishcloth and bar dish soap. 
A one stop shop for all@your plastic free needs is @packagefreeshop !!!
.
.
.
#plasticfreejuly #eliminatesingleuseplastic #savethesea #savetheocean #oceanplastic #singleuseplastic

One of the best parts of creating the @100footwave doc was seeing all the old imagery form around the world.
This is from Ryan Casey @deepwaterfilms . A brother that believed and filmed with us in Alaska Tahiti Hawai’i and he even got the XXL biggest wave of the year paddle video of me at Mavericks.  RIP Love you always!!! 
.
Teahupo’o with my brother @raimanaworld Love you brother!!!
After glacier surfing in 2007 I couldn’t really get the rush in the ocean anymore and I figured I might have a shot at getting the rush riding behind somebody.  In Tahiti Raimana was kind enough to share this wave with me. Something so special about sharing a big tube with a friend or a big wave with a friend as long as you both agree to it and your having a good time.
Definitely one of my most memorable waves of all time. Again love you Raimana!!!
.
And my brothers for life for towing me in, either @kealiihawaii or @ikaikakalama or maybe someone for towing me in ?? 😬 too many wipeouts I can’t remember 
.
